      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARE WEASLEY (10) was held up for a clear run at his latest appearance so prepared to forgive that result. Cops a similar draw so will require better luck but enjoys a drop in grade and had looked close to a win when placed in his previous two outings. MYNAMEISRUBY (7) draws wide but is going well having put five placings together, two of them from this same barrier. Up in grade but looks ready to strike if things go her way. TEX GOES BANG (12) raced parked at Maryborough last start but proved too strong, arriving 2.5 metres ahead of his rivals. Draws out on the second line so may need luck but if it comes his way he can feature again along with ATOMIC GLORY (6) who came from this barrier when placed last start at Maryborough.",
